01:34:43.513 --> 01:34:48.347
We are here because you signed a...

1038
01:34:49.138 --> 01:34:52.972
Because the local bakery
hired some foreign citizens.


1039
01:34:53.138 --> 01:34:57.472
Legally employed, not migrants,
like the village rumor says.


1040
01:34:58.138 --> 01:35:03.222
And you, the citizens, made a petition
demanding that they leave.


1041
01:35:03.513 --> 01:35:05.638
Who signed it?
Read out the names!


1042
01:35:05.805 --> 01:35:07.888
- Do you have the list?
- Yes.


1043
01:35:08.055 --> 01:35:12.805
Németh Zsolt, Kelemen Tibor,
Cipariu Aurica, Auner Matthias,


1044
01:35:13.222 --> 01:35:15.222
Teodorescu Avram, 
Iancu Áron...

1045
01:35:15.388 --> 01:35:18.472
Listen, I didn't put my name
on any list.


1046
01:35:18.638 --> 01:35:21.430
- I don't even care.
- That's just it!


1047
01:35:21.597 --> 01:35:24.055
There are 395 signatures.

1048
01:35:24.555 --> 01:35:27.055
You really want to hear all the names?

1049
01:35:27.222 --> 01:35:28.722
It's 411.

1050
01:35:31.013 --> 01:35:34.347
Please make a copy
and post it for all to see!


1051
01:35:34.513 --> 01:35:36.888
We'll pin it to the notice board.

1052
01:35:37.055 --> 01:35:42.263
There is also a list of names of those
who want these people to stay.


1053
01:35:42.430 --> 01:35:43.597
Who are they?

1054
01:35:43.763 --> 01:35:45.930
Me, Szabó Csilla,

1055
01:35:46.097 --> 01:35:49.388
Dénes Viktória, Amzulescu Traian,
Steffi Auner, Nagy Réka,


1056
01:35:49.555 --> 01:35:50.805
Németh Kinga,
your sister...


1057
01:35:50.972 --> 01:35:53.888
They're bakery employees!

1058
01:35:54.138 --> 01:35:56.513
- What?
- You made them sign!


1059
01:35:56.680 --> 01:35:57.930
No one made them.

1060
01:35:58.097 --> 01:36:01.138
Knowing the foreign workers personally,

1061
01:36:01.305 --> 01:36:03.138
they took the initiative.

1062
01:36:03.305 --> 01:36:05.930
Some even commute from Bradu.

1063
01:36:06.097 --> 01:36:08.597
I work here,
I'm entitled to an opinion!


1064
01:36:08.763 --> 01:36:11.138
How many names on the list?

1065
01:36:11.347 --> 01:36:14.513
28, but we only started it this morning.

1066
01:36:14.805 --> 01:36:16.097
Forget it!

1067
01:36:16.263 --> 01:36:17.555
Please, people!

1068
01:36:17.722 --> 01:36:20.805
When we don't like the outcome,
suddenly we don't want democracy!


1069
01:36:20.972 --> 01:36:25.513
395 for, 28 against.
Why are we still here?


1070
01:36:26.222 --> 01:36:27.930
411.

1071
01:36:28.097 --> 01:36:29.638
Please, let's start.

1072
01:36:29.805 --> 01:36:31.888
- Mrs. Miklós.
- May I?


1073
01:36:32.513 --> 01:36:34.263
Closer to the mic!

1074
01:36:34.430 --> 01:36:39.513
We have nothing against these people,
as long as they stay in their country,


1075
01:36:39.680 --> 01:36:44.138
not in our bakery
sticking their hands in bread we eat.


1076
01:36:44.305 --> 01:36:47.805
Call me old fashioned,
but it makes me sick.


1077
01:36:47.972 --> 01:36:48.888
Me too!

1078
01:36:49.055 --> 01:36:52.888
Let's stop buying from them
until they throw them out!


1079
01:36:53.805 --> 01:36:55.972
Seriously now, Mayor!

1080
01:36:56.138 --> 01:37:00.513
Why not?
Maybe an outside standpoint could help.


1081
01:37:01.638 --> 01:37:04.263
First of all, who is he?

1082
01:37:05.222 --> 01:37:08.680
He's from a French NGO
for conservation...


1083
01:37:16.013 --> 01:37:19.263
He's here to help
count the bear population.


1084
01:37:19.430 --> 01:37:21.180
Does anyone need a translation?

1085
01:37:21.347 --> 01:37:24.597
- Does he get paid for it?
- I don't know.


1086
01:37:26.055 --> 01:37:28.722
How much is he
paid to count our bears?

1087
01:37:28.888 --> 01:37:31.013
No idea, he's not on our payroll.

1088
01:37:31.180 --> 01:37:32.888
It's a matter of principle!

1089
01:37:33.055 --> 01:37:35.930
We're jobless,
the mine got shut down...


1090
01:37:36.097 --> 01:37:37.222
By ecologists!

1091
01:37:37.388 --> 01:37:41.638
Animals attack our livestock,
and he gets paid to count our bears?


1092
01:37:41.805 --> 01:37:44.222
He can count them in his own country!

1093
01:37:46.222 --> 01:37:48.180
They don't have any more bears,

1094
01:37:48.347 --> 01:37:51.097
they killed them all to build freeways!

1095
01:37:51.263 --> 01:37:52.430
Same with the wolves!

1096
01:37:52.597 --> 01:37:55.597
So they got all developed

1097
01:37:55.763 --> 01:37:58.930
and now they tell us
to be Europe's zoo?


1098
01:38:00.138 --> 01:38:02.263
Like they did in Africa!

1099
01:38:02.430 --> 01:38:03.930
Only we're not savages!

1100
01:38:04.097 --> 01:38:07.805
Please!
Will you let the man speak?


1101
01:38:08.472 --> 01:38:09.680
Order!

1102
01:38:10.430 --> 01:38:11.305
Merci.

1103
01:38:16.222 --> 01:38:20.097
We noticed. In Paris there are
more Blacks and Arabs than French!


1104
01:38:20.263 --> 01:38:22.597
It makes you afraid to use the metro!

1105
01:38:25.138 --> 01:38:28.847
You wanted colonies, now handle them!

1106
01:38:29.013 --> 01:38:31.430
But why do we
have to pay for it?

1107
01:38:39.388 --> 01:38:44.430
I don't believe
you've seen any Hungarians begging!


1108
01:38:44.763 --> 01:38:47.680
Nor Romanians!
Those are Gypsies!


1109
01:38:47.847 --> 01:38:50.180
Let's make this distinction, please!

1110
01:38:50.513 --> 01:38:52.638
The Roma are citizens too.

1111
01:38:52.805 --> 01:38:55.430
So listen, Mr. Fraternité
-Egalité...

1112
01:38:55.597 --> 01:38:59.555
If you love them so much,
why do you keep sending them back?


1113
01:39:04.430 --> 01:39:08.763
There's no integrating Gypsies,
why beat around the bush?


1114
01:39:09.138 --> 01:39:10.930
Order, please!

1115
01:39:11.513 --> 01:39:16.013
So integrate your Blacks and Arabs
if you're so good at it!


1116
01:39:19.680 --> 01:39:22.597
- They'll soon slit your throats!
- Serves you right!


1117
01:39:22.763 --> 01:39:26.888
You didn't learn from Charlie Hebdo!
You have nothing sacred!


1118
01:39:27.055 --> 01:39:32.180
Please, let's put this aside
and return to our business.


1119
01:39:32.472 --> 01:39:35.805
- Civilly, without offending.
- Who's offending anyone?


1120
01:39:35.972 --> 01:39:39.638
- Now we can't tell the truth?
- Communism all over again!


1121
01:39:39.805 --> 01:39:42.430
You get punished
for speaking your mind.


1122
01:39:42.597 --> 01:39:46.222
Please, let's get back to the subject!

1123
01:39:46.430 --> 01:39:48.597
We are on the subject!

1124
01:39:48.763 --> 01:39:51.013
We've seen it in other countries.

1125
01:39:51.180 --> 01:39:52.888
First there's one or two,

1126
01:39:53.055 --> 01:39:55.472
then they bring the whole family!

1127
01:39:55.930 --> 01:39:57.930
It's their custom!

1128
01:39:58.097 --> 01:39:59.805
Then they want mosques!

1129
01:39:59.972 --> 01:40:03.180
In Germany you can't even enter
their neighborhoods!


1130
01:40:03.347 --> 01:40:06.597
They attack women in the street
for not wearing a veil!


1131
01:40:06.763 --> 01:40:10.555
I hardly think we need to fear that
in our village.


1132
01:40:10.722 --> 01:40:15.055
Not yet, but if they keep coming,
won't they end up asking for rights?


1133
01:40:15.222 --> 01:40:16.763
With bombings and whatnot?

1134
01:40:16.930 --> 01:40:19.263
Out with them! 
Kick them out!

1135
01:40:19.680 --> 01:40:22.888
Rest assured, in our neck of the woods,

1136
01:40:23.055 --> 01:40:27.847
we wouldn't make the news
even if they blew us all up!


1137
01:40:28.222 --> 01:40:29.430
Talk about what?

1138
01:40:29.972 --> 01:40:33.055
Please, Doctor,
just stick to the subject.


1139
01:40:33.972 --> 01:40:36.888
I only have one observation to make.

1140
01:40:37.305 --> 01:40:39.847
I don't know
the gentlemen from Bangladesh...


1141
01:40:40.013 --> 01:40:41.263
Sri Lanka!

1142
01:40:41.472 --> 01:40:44.513
Sri Lanka.
They may be very clean.


1143
01:40:44.680 --> 01:40:47.680
I'll say this in Romanian
for all to understand.


1144
01:40:48.138 --> 01:40:49.763
Asian pathology is different...

1145
01:40:49.930 --> 01:40:51.888
At least give me your hand.

1146
01:40:52.055 --> 01:40:56.972
Same as their diseases,
their viruses, their immune reactions.


1147
01:40:57.138 --> 01:41:00.847
That's how this planet
got AIDS, bird flu,


1148
01:41:01.013 --> 01:41:03.388
and who knows what else next!

1149
01:41:03.555 --> 01:41:06.763
From communities
who come into direct contact


1150
01:41:06.930 --> 01:41:09.930
with animals: monkeys, bears, bats...

1151
01:41:10.097 --> 01:41:14.180
Then they spread it,
because they're free to circulate!


1152
01:41:14.430 --> 01:41:15.430
Doctor,

1153
01:41:15.597 --> 01:41:19.305
they had a full set of tests
before employment.


1154
01:41:22.305 --> 01:41:24.180
If I may!

1155
01:41:24.847 --> 01:41:27.138
This is about hygiene.

1156
01:41:27.305 --> 01:41:31.222
Pardon me, but Muslims don't
wipe their butts like the rest of us.


1157
01:41:32.263 --> 01:41:34.305
And in a bakery...

1158
01:41:34.472 --> 01:41:36.805
- They're not Muslim!
- Even so!


1159
01:41:36.972 --> 01:41:39.388
Please!
Mr. Baciu.


1160
01:41:39.680 --> 01:41:41.888
I have one last thing to say.

1161
01:41:42.180 --> 01:41:44.638
Our end won't come from the atomic bomb.

1162
01:41:44.805 --> 01:41:49.097
It will come from
all these wretches swarming us,


1163
01:41:49.388 --> 01:41:54.347
as we build parks in villages on EU funds
and measure cucumbers with calipers!


1164
01:41:54.513 --> 01:41:56.638
Your cucumber
is easy enough to measure!


1165
01:41:56.805 --> 01:42:00.305
Truth be told,
why did we need a park in the village?


1166
01:42:00.472 --> 01:42:02.472
I can answer that.

1167
01:42:02.638 --> 01:42:06.222
We access the available EU funds.

1168
01:42:06.388 --> 01:42:08.680
And the ones for village parks
were available.


1169
01:42:08.847 --> 01:42:12.888
Why not sewage first?
And paved streets?


1170
01:42:13.055 --> 01:42:16.597
Because there were no funds for that!

1171
01:42:16.763 --> 01:42:21.597
Besides, with the funding for parks
we installed street lighting.


1172
01:42:21.763 --> 01:42:24.388
I've had my hand up
since the start!


1173
01:42:24.555 --> 01:42:27.763
- But to the subject.
- Sure, Mayor.


1174
01:42:27.930 --> 01:42:29.847
My name is Brebu Vasile.

1175
01:42:30.013 --> 01:42:33.930
For those who don't know me,
I used to work at the bakery.


1176
01:42:34.222 --> 01:42:35.722
I think the problem is:

1177
01:42:35.888 --> 01:42:39.472
Why hire foreigners for our jobs?

1178
01:42:39.847 --> 01:42:41.888
Because our folks don't want to work!

1179
01:42:42.055 --> 01:42:44.347
And why don't they?

1180
01:42:44.513 --> 01:42:46.513
They'd rather live on social aid!

1181
01:42:49.013 --> 01:42:51.263
Not true. Allow me to differ.

1182
01:42:51.430 --> 01:42:54.097
Sure, there's a bad apple
in every crate.


1183
01:42:54.263 --> 01:42:58.263
But most of us work hard
in any country they go to.


1184
01:42:58.972 --> 01:43:03.305
You all know it,
work abroad is tough work.


1185
01:43:03.555 --> 01:43:06.597
A foreigner who hires you
does it to exploit you!


1186
01:43:08.930 --> 01:43:10.388
They pay, though!

1187
01:43:10.555 --> 01:43:13.388
Exactly, dear sir, thank you!

1188
01:43:13.555 --> 01:43:18.680
The question is:
Why does this company pay so little?


1189
01:43:19.097 --> 01:43:22.597
Why doesn't it pay overtime?

1190
01:43:22.930 --> 01:43:24.847
Of course we pay it!

1191
01:43:25.013 --> 01:43:30.888
Not true! I have 43 hours
of unpaid overtime I sued you for.


1192
01:43:31.138 --> 01:43:35.680
This is verifiable, we've been paying
all overtime since 2018.


1193
01:43:35.847 --> 01:43:38.430
Don't you tell me that,

1194
01:43:38.597 --> 01:43:40.513
I'm an old employee.

1195
01:43:40.680 --> 01:43:43.013
I know the overtime and the holidays

1196
01:43:43.180 --> 01:43:46.263
that I worked with no pay!

1197
01:43:46.972 --> 01:43:49.847
- Mr. Brebu...
- Wait!


1198
01:43:50.055 --> 01:43:52.597
I know all the other workers
feel the same


1199
01:43:52.763 --> 01:43:55.722
but don't dare to say it.

1200
01:43:56.180 --> 01:43:58.347
For fear they'll be fired!

1201
01:44:00.680 --> 01:44:03.472
The job ads were around for weeks!

1202
01:44:03.638 --> 01:44:06.555
- We're desperate to hire...
- On minimum wage!


1203
01:44:06.722 --> 01:44:09.347
You'd rather a loaf cost 5 lei?

1204
01:44:09.513 --> 01:44:11.055
Why not 10?

1205
01:44:11.222 --> 01:44:15.055
A bakery is hard work for little pay,

1206
01:44:15.222 --> 01:44:17.888
including holidays,
because people want fresh bread.


1207
01:44:18.055 --> 01:44:18.972
True.

1208
01:44:19.138 --> 01:44:20.972
- So that's how it is?
- Yes.


1209
01:44:21.138 --> 01:44:24.513
How come it's not the same for you?

1210
01:44:24.888 --> 01:44:27.888
How much was your fancy Mercedes?

1211
01:44:29.013 --> 01:44:32.347
While you pay workers the minimum wage!

1212
01:44:32.513 --> 01:44:34.305
The car is on lease.

1213
01:44:34.680 --> 01:44:37.722
On the backs of your workers, Madam!

1214
01:44:37.888 --> 01:44:40.430
The Reverend has a Mercedes too!

1215
01:44:42.138 --> 01:44:44.430
It belongs to my mom.

1216
01:44:45.430 --> 01:44:47.347
And it was second-hand.

1217
01:44:47.513 --> 01:44:50.055
Please, we're drifting off the subject.

1218
01:44:50.222 --> 01:44:55.180
Thank you, Mr. Brebu,
we were not aware of these complaints.


1219
01:44:55.388 --> 01:44:58.972
Allow me, accusations have been made...

1220
01:44:59.138 --> 01:45:01.222
In Romanian, please!

1221
01:45:03.013 --> 01:45:04.430
Look.

1222
01:45:04.972 --> 01:45:10.180
In the last four years,
we've created most local jobs.


1223
01:45:11.805 --> 01:45:14.305
We also support the local music club

1224
01:45:14.472 --> 01:45:17.347
and want to keep supporting the region.

1225
01:45:17.513 --> 01:45:20.222
As such, we applied for EU funds.

1226
01:45:20.388 --> 01:45:24.513
- Not like you did it for us!
- The money will be spent here.


1227
01:45:24.680 --> 01:45:26.722
The money you don't pocket!

1228
01:45:26.888 --> 01:45:29.472
Please, we're off the subject again!

1229
01:45:29.680 --> 01:45:32.055
Let's put it to the vote.

1230
01:45:32.513 --> 01:45:37.055
Those in favor of our jobs being
available to foreigners brought here?


1231
01:45:37.888 --> 01:45:39.597
That's clear enough.

1232
01:45:39.763 --> 01:45:41.305
Matthias, please.

1233
01:45:45.222 --> 01:45:47.347
I didn't quite understand that.

1234
01:45:47.513 --> 01:45:50.638
He asked who's in favor
of the foreigners staying.


1235
01:45:51.680 --> 01:45:54.388
The question wasn't very well-phrased.

1236
01:45:54.555 --> 01:45:56.347
It was plenty well-phrased!

1237
01:45:56.513 --> 01:46:01.472
We're afraid of public opinion,
but most of us don't want them here!


1238
01:46:03.305 --> 01:46:06.847
Here's my proposal
to defuse the situation.


1239
01:46:07.013 --> 01:46:10.305
We give the foreign workers gloves...

1240
01:46:13.555 --> 01:46:18.388
Or we move them to other positions,
where they don't touch the dough.


1241
01:46:18.555 --> 01:46:21.472
We don't want them,
what the hell isn't clear?


1242
01:46:21.638 --> 01:46:24.597
Then we'll lodge them
in another village.


1243
01:46:24.763 --> 01:46:27.347
No, they should just leave!

1244
01:46:29.180 --> 01:46:33.055
Who wants to stop buying their bread
until they throw them out?


1245
01:46:34.680 --> 01:46:37.472
This country still has laws, you know!

1246
01:46:37.638 --> 01:46:41.347
That's why we want autonomy,
so we don't get told what to do.


1247
01:46:41.513 --> 01:46:45.180
I wonder how you Hungarians,
a minority in our country,


1248
01:46:45.347 --> 01:46:47.263
discriminate against other foreigners!

1249
01:46:49.638 --> 01:46:51.430
Auner Matthias!

1250
01:46:53.305 --> 01:46:55.055
Matthias, where are you?

1251
01:46:56.930 --> 01:46:58.513
Matthias. Go home.

1252
01:46:58.680 --> 01:47:02.055
- What happened?
- Papa Otto hanged himself!


1253
01:48:22.930 --> 01:48:24.597
May God rest him in peace.

1254
01:48:31.180 --> 01:48:32.388
Help me.

1255
01:48:46.555 --> 01:48:48.472
I love you, Dad.

1256
01:48:48.638 --> 01:48:49.972
I love you.

1257
01:49:54.347 --> 01:49:57.805
We have to reapply to
the "under 30 employees" category.


1258
01:49:57.972 --> 01:49:59.013
There's no time.

1259
01:49:59.180 --> 01:50:02.555
Stop the production.
We'll do it all together tonight.


1260
01:50:02.722 --> 01:50:05.513
Two more workers
are due to arrive tonight.


1261
01:50:05.680 --> 01:50:08.347
- We'll have to cancel.
- We can't just...


1262
01:50:08.513 --> 01:50:11.763
What else can we do in this situation?

1263
01:50:13.263 --> 01:50:17.013
- These are humans we're talking about.
- I'm perfectly aware.


1264
01:50:17.180 --> 01:50:19.722
But we're humans too.

1265
01:50:19.888 --> 01:50:23.805
With no more clients,
all we've built these 10 years will fall.


1266
01:50:23.972 --> 01:50:25.763
And they'll be jobless.

1267
01:50:25.930 --> 01:50:28.180
No one will be left jobless.

1268
01:50:29.513 --> 01:50:33.930
Sure, you'll find new jobs
and I'll be left with all the debt.


1269
01:50:35.638 --> 01:50:38.388
So please get to work
on the application.


1270
01:50:42.013 --> 01:50:43.763
I'm not redoing it.

1271
01:50:45.013 --> 01:50:48.638
They have families, contracts,
we can't trample it all.


1272
01:50:48.805 --> 01:50:50.763
No one's trampling anything.

1273
01:50:51.138 --> 01:50:54.930
I spoke with the mayor, they'll sleep
at the police station tonight.


1274
01:50:55.138 --> 01:50:58.722
Tomorrow we move them to Bradu.
Let them know.


1275
01:51:05.513 --> 01:51:08.055
I got a job offer in Germany.

1276
01:51:09.638 --> 01:51:13.763
I wasn't going to take it,
but as things are, I quit right now.


1277
01:51:18.222 --> 01:51:22.097
You were the last one
who hadn't stabbed me in the back.


1278
